---
title: Hot Honey Halloumi Tacos with Avocado Salad & Garlic Aioli
description: We’re all jumping on the hot honey trend - it’s the perfect combination of sweet and spice that gets our mouths watering. Why not drizzle it on salty halloumi, for an extra dimension of flavour? Pack all of that goodness into warm tacos with a simple avocado salad for a whole new twist on tacos.
